<detall><id label=""><![CDATA[77424]]></id><title label="Titol"><![CDATA[Viure sota vidre [Living under glass], at the círcol Maldà]]></title><excerpt label="Resum"><![CDATA[Three old friends are reunited and discover what still unites them today and what separates them from their shared past.]]></excerpt><content label="Contingut"><![CDATA[<p>Jeani, Babsi and Max, three friends from university, meet up again after a long time apart to spend a weekend together.Each one of them has different reasons for getting back in touch with the others, but a cloud heavy with expectations and resentment hangs over their heads and prevents them from finding the intimacy they enjoyed years earlier.Through a lack of communication, irony and desire, they discover what it is that still unites them in the present and what separates them from their shared past.</p>
